 <span data-ttu-id="797fb-106"><xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen>類別即可顯示支援 Windows 影像處理元件 (WIC) 任何影像格式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="797fb-106">The <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen> class can display any image format that is supported by the Windows Imaging Component (WIC).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="797fb-107">例如，您可以使用 BMP、 GIF、 JPEG、 PNG 或 TIFF 格式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="797fb-107">For example, you can use the BMP, GIF, JPEG, PNG, or TIFF format.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="797fb-108">如果影像是 PNG 檔案，而且它會包含 alpha 色板，影像會轉譯使用 alpha 色板中定義的透明度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="797fb-108">If the image is a PNG file and it includes an alpha channel, the image is rendered using the transparency defined in the alpha channel.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="797fb-109">您不能包含預留位置文字中要於稍後加入您的程式碼啟動顯示畫面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="797fb-109">You cannot include placeholder text in the splash screen that is later added by your code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="797fb-110">如果您想要在啟動顯示畫面中包含文字，您必須將它加入至映像檔案。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="797fb-110">If you want to include text in the splash screen, you must add it to the image file.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="797fb-111">您不需要撰寫任何程式碼，以顯示啟動顯示畫面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="797fb-111">It is not necessary to write any code to display a splash screen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="797fb-112">從開始[!INCLUDE[vs_orcas_long](~/includes/vs-orcas-long-md.md)]SP1，您可以快速設定啟動顯示畫面以預設設定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="797fb-112">Starting in [!INCLUDE[vs_orcas_long](~/includes/vs-orcas-long-md.md)] SP1, you can quickly configure a splash screen with default settings.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="797fb-113">如需詳細資訊，請參閱[How to: WPF 應用程式中加入啟動顯示畫面](~/docs/framework/wpf/app-development/how-to-add-a-splash-screen-to-a-wpf-application.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="797fb-113">For more information, see [How to: Add a Splash Screen to a WPF Application](~/docs/framework/wpf/app-development/how-to-add-a-splash-screen-to-a-wpf-application.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="797fb-114"><xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen>類別後，會顯示啟動顯示畫面儘速在啟動應用程式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="797fb-114">The <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen> class displays the splash screen as soon as possible after the application is started.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="797fb-115">建立 WPF 應用程式執行個體之前，請使用原生程式碼，會顯示啟動顯示畫面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="797fb-115">The splash screen is displayed by using native code, before the WPF application instance is created.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="797fb-116">啟動顯示畫面會顯示在螢幕中央。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="797fb-116">The splash screen is displayed in the center of the screen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="797fb-117">載入應用程式時，啟動顯示畫面會淡入。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="797fb-117">When the application is loaded, the splash screen fades.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="797fb-118">當您的應用程式編譯時，影像內嵌為受管理的資源組件中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="797fb-118">When your application is compiled, the image is embedded as a managed resource in the assembly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="797fb-119">如果應用程式當地語系化時，影像會內嵌在當地語系化的附屬 DLL。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="797fb-119">If the application is localized, the image is embedded in the localized satellite DLL.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
